	someicon
	($ cname .. " 'fahrt durch den Wald in der Nacht hinein. " .. cHe .. "  In English:  takes a wrong turn and hits the end of the road. Nearby to the north, " .. che .. " kann kaum die Form einer Hutte erkennen." $) cyoa-text! basic-tone
